# LLM Plugin (sh-shp-llm) Memory

## Overview
SelfHelp LLM plugin at `server/plugins/sh-shp-llm/`. Provides AI chat, LLM scripts, admin console, and response components. Built with PHP backend + React 18 TypeScript frontend compiled to UMD bundles via Vite.

